name: Sage Watches Jolm
description: After Jolm long journey into the mystical world of Iyusmn and meeting with Una, Jolm travel continues to a dry warm desert. Jolm felt something strange. Something or someone was following Jolm, it felt like something was watching Jolm from the distance. Then, at some point, the watcher appearance became vivid and turned out it is the eye watcher, Sage. She controls all the living things there and give them life in the dry and barren land.
